window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The dragon king told me to stay away from him. I didn't listen.</b></p> <p>When the king of this realm saw me bathing in a stream, he did his best to warn me. Keep my distance, or the curse upon him would set his blood on fire, and he would ravage me brutally.</p> <p>I didn't, and he did.</p> <p>But he did more than just pin me to the forest floor and mount me like a feral beast.</p> <p>He made me his, and no matter how savagely he ruts me or how thoroughly he blisters my bare backside while trying to scare me away, I'll never stop being what I was always destined to be.</p> <p>His mate.</p> <p>Feral King<i> is a standalone novel and book three of the Dragonborne Kings series. Intended for mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
